headline: Morgan Stanley updated its growth stocks portfolio. Here are the latest changes
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley made several notable adjustments to its U.S. All Cap Growth model portfolio, increasing exposure to semiconductors and software while exiting positions in healthcare and restaurants.
